#

Spinach Salad with Grilled Chicken and Balsamic Dressing

30 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

SaladHealthyEasy

Description

A refreshing and nutritious spinach salad topped with grilled chicken, cherry tomatoes, and a tangy balsamic vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • grilled chicken breast: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1
  • red onion: 1/4
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • balsamic vinaigrette: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
